00:03:27.007 --> 00:03:56.279
What you're about to see are things that I have been praying over for the last six months or so about Israel, the Jonathan relationship, and praying over the Strait—the passageway where all the oil tankers come through—and praying over strategic strikes against Iran to make them where they don't have nuclear capabilities.

