Thank you for watching this; I hope this blesses you all. Right after that, I'm going to tell you all about the Dinar and what the Lord has showed me.

00:04:02.943 --> 00:04:30.279
I saw in the land of prophecies, Israel, and in that sea where Israel owns a massive reservoir of oil and natural gas that will be tapped into; it's worth billions and billions over the next four years.

00:04:30.280 --> 00:04:39.724
