00:04:39.725 --> 00:04:50.448
I don't know if they're oranges—I don't even know if they grow oranges, folks—but I saw fruit that was ginormous and vegetables that were beautiful and healthy.

00:04:50.449 --> 00:05:01.937
The Lord said it's the Abrahamic Covenant, a supernatural breathing on it, an evidence showing that God is God over Israel.

00:05:01.938 --> 00:05:11.088
It will come through blessing, favor, and wealth as America backs it, and favor and blessing and wealth come on America.

00:05:11.089 --> 00:05:20.757
